<h3>Help - myIATA Operational Desk Portal</h3>
<table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" width="95%" border="0" class="basictable"><thead><tr class="Whsep Wvsep"><td>Account Management - Profile Defination</td>
</tr>
</thead><tbody><tr><td><h3><strong>Purpose:</strong></h3>
<p>This screen facilitates assigning of roles for existing Profiles across applications. New profiles can also be created.</p>
<p>While the Role definition characterizes the functional accessibility within applications, Profiles definition describes the roles that can be assigned for different applications.</p>
<h3><strong>Actions:</strong></h3>
<ul><li>Select the required Profile from the drop down menu. <ul><li>Existing Profile for modifications</li>
<li>Create New Profile - to add a new profile.</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li>Depending on this selection the further tabs will appear.</li>
</ul>
<h4><strong>Existing Profile</strong></h4>
<ul><li>Data is pre-populated and the assigned roles are fetched based on the profile selected.</li>
<li>Click on <strong>Save Changes</strong> to save all the changes made.</li>
<li>Click on <strong>Cancel Changes</strong> to discard all actions.</li>
<li>Click on <strong>Delete Role</strong> to remove the selected role.</li>
<li>For <strong>Assigning Roles</strong> please refer to <a href="http://localhost:80/PortalDocroot/cms/sites/default/static/content/en/application/portal/help/ODP/Portal_User_Management_External_User_Edit_Roles.htm">Set User Roles</a> .</li>
</ul>
<h4><strong>Add New role</strong></h4>
<ul><li>Make the various selection by choosing/entering the relevant options <ul><li><strong>Profile Type</strong> <strong>:</strong> Select the profile from the drop down list.</li>
<li><strong>User Type:</strong> Select the desired option.</li>
<li><strong>Profile Name:</strong> Enter the name for the profile.</li>
<li><strong>Description:</strong> Enter the description for the profile being created</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li>For <strong>Assigning Roles</strong> please refer to <a href="http://localhost:80/PortalDocroot/cms/sites/default/static/content/en/application/portal/help/ODP/Portal_User_Management_External_User_Edit_Roles.htm">Set User Roles</a> .</li>
<li>Click on <strong>Save Changes</strong> to save all the changes made.</li>
<li>Click on <strong>Cancel Changes</strong> to discard all actions.</li>
</ul>
</td>
</tr>
</tbody></table>
